eleven.biography: Has telekinetic powers and a mysterious past. Loves Eggo waffles and protecting her friends from the Upside Down.

will.biography: Experienced the horrors of the Upside Down. Often quiet and thoughtful, and has a knack for survival.

mike.biography: Loyal friend and leader of the group. Always ready to face supernatural dangers to protect his friends.

dustin.biography: Energetic and clever. Loves science, science fairs, and uncovering mysteries with his friends.

eddie.biography: Fun-loving and rebellious. Plays in a metal band and stands up for what he believes in.

vecna.biography: Mysterious and sinister entity from the Upside Down, feared by all who know of him.

billy.biography: Cocky and athletic. Has a tough exterior but a complicated family life.

steve.biography: From a former high school heartthrob to a loyal babysitter and friend, wielding a baseball bat against monsters.

max.biography: Skater girl with a sharp wit. Brave and resourceful when it comes to supernatural threats.

nancy.biography: Curious and determined. Investigates mysteries and isn’t afraid to stand up to danger.

jim.biography: Hawkins’ chief of police. Stern but caring, always trying to protect the town from supernatural threats.

lucas.biography: Brave and resourceful. Skilled with strategy and makes tough choices to help his friends.

joey.biography: Charming and goofy. Loves food and friends, often providing comic relief in tense moments.

rachel.biography: Fashion-forward and ambitious. Cares deeply for her friends and navigates life with style and grace.

chandler.biography: Sarcastic and witty. Uses humor to navigate awkward situations and support friends through tough times.

phoebe.biography: Eccentric and musical. Believes in spirits and mystical things, with a heart full of compassion.

ross.biography: Intelligent and a bit neurotic. Obsessed with paleontology and the details of everyday life.

monica.biography: Competitive and perfectionist. Loves cooking and cleaning, always striving to be the best.

leslie.biography: Ambitious and organized. Passionate about public service and making her community better.

ron.biography: Stoic and private. Loves woodworking, breakfast meats, and avoiding unnecessary bureaucracy.

april.biography: Deadpan and sarcastic. Prefers to keep people at a distance but is fiercely loyal to those she trusts.

andy.biography: Goofy and fun-loving. Has a big heart and a love for music, despite not always being competent.

ben.biography: Responsible and practical. Often the voice of reason in his social circle, with a love for rules and order.

ann.biography: Friendly and caring. Devoted to helping friends and keeping relationships strong.

tom.biography: Charismatic and ambitious. Loves the spotlight and has a knack for entrepreneurship.

jerry.biography: Kind-hearted but bumbling. Often the target of jokes, but always tries his best.

donna.biography: Confident and stylish. Enjoys luxury and the finer things in life, while keeping friends entertained.

chris.biography: Overly enthusiastic and extremely positive. Tries to motivate everyone around him with energy and optimism.

eleanor.biography: Self-centered but gradually learns empathy. Finds herself in morally complex situations but grows over time.

chidi.biography: Ethical and indecisive. Constantly agonizes over making the right choice, often overthinking everything.

tahani.biography: Elegant and glamorous. Loves hosting and being admired, but secretly craves genuine connection.

jason.biography: Energetic and confident. Often makes mistakes but is always learning from them.

michael.biography: Meticulous and rule-focused. Strives to do everything perfectly, often acting as a voice of reason.
